	Author book ?

Offer mining [] will add a mining skill use to the list
of skills which a mining guild offers.

A guild may only offer skills within the same skill
family.  The skill school must be offered by the guild
before any subskill can be added.

For instance, Offer mining must first be used on skill
129 before any of the mining subskill can be added to
the guild.

